All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public class JDialogDataIDProperties
extends javax.swing.JDialog
JDialogDataIDProperties class is used to amend the APP_MATERIAL_DATA_IDS table. The default APP_MATERIAL table holds the basic material master data. However in order to extend the type of data which can be stored and also link it so a customer there is another table called APP_MATERIAL_CUSTOMER_DATA. This second table is keyed on MATERIAL, CUSTOMER_ID and DATA_ID. The DATA_ID can be anything meaningful name to describe the new data item being stored.

See Also:
JInternalFrameDataIDAdmin, JDBDataIDs, Serialized Form
